name: Dissolving Painting 7 - Wanderer [Ovoo]
description:
On the threshold of the unknown, the cold wind, and the endless sky. I cherish those who wander in their search of new paths. 
When traveling, it is custom to stop and circle an ovoo three times, moving clockwise, in order to have a safer journey. 
By RubenFro - Twitter: @Ruben_Fro
